Ubuntu indicator applet for toggl web app
Displays current and recent tasks from www.toggl.com account

Features:
 * Display active and recent tasks
 * Click to start and stop tasks
 * Create new tasks 
 * Notification reminder of currently active task

Running:
 * get API_KEY from Settings -> My Account section of toggle webapp
 * python indicator-applet-toggl.py <API_KEY>

Todo:
  * Need configuration screens and files 
  * Support for tags in Create Task screen
  * Sort out custom icon and setup process

Known Issues:
 * Currently not packaged as an app, should be executed using
   python indicator-applet-toggl.py
